四、调包使用sklearn的逻辑回归¶

In [2]:
from time import time
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

from sklearn import linear_model
from sklearn import datasets
from sklearn.svm import l1_min_c

iris = datasets.load_iris()
X = iris.data
y = iris.target

X = X[y != 2]
y = y[y != 2]

X /= X.max()  # Normalize X to speed-up convergence



cs = l1_min_c(X, y, loss="log") * np.logspace(0, 7, 16)


print("Computing regularization path ...")
start = time()
clf = linear_model.LogisticRegression(
    penalty="l1",
    solver="liblinear",
    tol=1e-6,
    max_iter=int(1e6),
    warm_start=True,
    intercept_scaling=10000.0,
)
coefs_ = []
for c in cs:
    clf.set_params(C=c)
    clf.fit(X, y)
    coefs_.append(clf.coef_.ravel().copy())
print("This took %0.3fs" % (time() - start))

coefs_ = np.array(coefs_)
plt.plot(np.log10(cs), coefs_, marker="o")
ymin, ymax = plt.ylim()
plt.xlabel("log(C)")
plt.ylabel("Coefficients")
plt.title("Logistic Regression Path")
plt.axis("tight")
plt.show()

五、再现ml0701_logit_stochastic_iris.py，调整学习率和迭代次数，展示不同参数下的结果。¶

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
from matplotlib.colors import ListedColormap
import pandas as pd
from sklearn.datasets import load_iris

cmap_light = ListedColormap(['#FFAAAA', '#AAFFAA', '#AAAAFF'])
cmap_bold = ListedColormap(['#FF0000', '#00FF00', '#0000FF'])


# 数据读入
def create_data():
    iris = load_iris()
    df = pd.DataFrame(iris.data, columns=iris.feature_names)
    df['label'] = iris.target
    df.columns = ['sepal length', 'sepal width', 'petal length', 'petal width', 'label']
    data = np.array(df.iloc[:100, [0, 1, -1]])
    # print(data)
    return data[:, :2], data[:, -1]


x, y = create_data()

# x加上截距项
b = np.ones([len(x), 1])
x = np.concatenate([x, b], 1)

# 随机初始化
omega = np.array([0., 0., 0.])
eta = 0.2


# 模型函数
def prob(xi, omega):
    exp = np.exp(np.dot(xi, omega))
    return exp / (1 + exp)


# 迭代次数控制停机
for ii in range(10000):
    for xi, yi in zip(x, y):
        g = (yi - prob(xi, omega)) * xi
        omega += eta * g
        # print(xi, yi, prob(xi, omega), g, omega)


# 结果展示
print(omega)

# 可视化展示
xx = np.linspace(np.min(x[:, 0]) - .1, np.max(x[:, 0]) + .1, 200)
yy = np.linspace(np.min(x[:, 1]) - .1, np.max(x[:, 1]) + .1, 200)

xx, yy = np.meshgrid(xx, yy)
Z = np.array([np.sign(prob(xi, omega) - 0.5) for xi in
              zip(xx.ravel(), yy.ravel(), np.ones(xx.shape).ravel())]).reshape(xx.shape)

plt.figure()
plt.pcolormesh(xx, yy, Z, cmap=cmap_light)  # 绘制预测结果图
plt.scatter(x[:, 0], x[:, 1], c=y, cmap=cmap_bold)
plt.grid()
plt.title('ml0701_logit_stochastic_iris')
